<br>
When i get quest items in the swamp of no hope, I am not going to go into Cab. so see if someone wants it.  I shout 2 times that if they are in need of it to tell me.  99.5% of the time I just give it to them, but if someone gets the items and wants to continue the hunt.  I am playing a monk.  With the low end items, the weight I have on my character &lt;without bags of any type&gt; is darn close to the limit.  If I pick up an 8 weight item that may benefit a warrior in the zone I am going to shout it...if no replies, I am going to destroy it because I want to keep the weight down.<br>
<br>
personal conversations...heh, no one really wants to hear em, unless you are trying to get some other folks to join in on the plot you are trying to develop or what ever.<br>
<br>
=) don't think that because people are shouting some of those things that they are not trying to remain in character.<br>
